Repeat: k3-tog, k3, yo, k1, yo, k2
k3-tog, k2, yo, k1, yo, k3

work a Long Eyelet Stitch Group in the eyelet 3 rows below next stitch; work a Long Eyelet Stitch Group in the eyelet 5 rows below the following stitch; work a Long Eyelet Stitch Group in the eyelet 7 rows below the 3rd stitch on the left needle; knit the next stitch on the left needle and pass each of the 9 Long Eyelet Stitch loops over the knit stitch; k8
